  "title": "Student Care Teacher",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Summary</strong></p><p>You will coach primary school students in English, Math, Science, Chinese, and assessment papers. You will supervise and support students in completing homework, ensure their well-being during meals and playtime, organize activities during school holidays, and prepare and mark learning papers.</p><p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Coach primary level students in English, Math, Science, Chinese, and assessment papers to improve their academic performance</li><li>Supervise students during homework sessions and provide guidance to help them complete assignments accurately</li><li>Monitor and support students’ well-being during meal and playtime to ensure a safe and positive environment</li><li>Organize and plan engaging activities during school holidays to enrich students’ learning experiences</li><li>Prepare and mark students’ learning papers to assess their understanding and progress</li></ul>",
